  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the current study is to demonstrate non-inferiority of everolimus-eluting
      bioresorbable vascular scaffold to everolimus-eluting stents in patients with chronic total
      occlusion regarding the antirestenotic efficacy at 8 to 10-month angiographic follow-up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
